Knora-ui modules

@knora/core

Requests ontology information from Knora.

method

getOntologiesMetadata()

Requests the metadata about all existing ontologies from Knora's ontologies route.

returns: the metadata of all ontologies (Observable of ApiServiceResult).
the metadata of all ontologies (Observable of ApiServiceResult).

method

getAllEntityDefinitionsForOntologies()

Requests all entity definitions for the given ontologies from Knora's ontologies route.

param: {string} ontologyIri the Iris of the named graphs whose resource classes are to be returned.
{string} ontologyIri the Iris of the named graphs whose resource classes are to be returned.
returns: the requested ontology (Observable of ApiServiceResult).
the requested ontology (Observable of ApiServiceResult).

method

getResourceClasses()

Requests information about the given resource classes from Knora's ontologies route.

param: {string[]} resourceClassIris the Iris of the resource classes to be queried.
{string[]} resourceClassIris the Iris of the resource classes to be queried.
returns: the requested resource class definitions (Observable of ApiServiceResult).
the requested resource class definitions (Observable of ApiServiceResult).
